{"tid":1703802,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"嚴正呼籲41校網勿參與明日三罷","createTime":"2019-11-10T12:25:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T15:33:40.000Z","uid":88284,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"aa318db09985350e69b3960512736dd13c56c0b9","tid":1703802,"uid":88284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T12:25:31.000Z","msg":"大家都知道41校網係名校區<br />\n位處九龍塘、畢架山道、廣播道等位置<br />\n入面大量高官、中產子女就讀<br />\n特別今日又一城班暴徒事件<br />\n如果暴徒堵晒路，甚至破壞學校<br />\n令中產校網成為第一批罷學既學校<br />\n一定會更易影響周邊罷學風氣<br />\n所以在此請各位勿令<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">41校網學校罷課</span></span>！！！<br />\np.s.附學校名單以作提醒<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.edb.gov.hk/attachment/tc/edu-system/primary-secondary/spa-systems/primary-1-admission/school-lists/2020dpnet-41.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.edb.gov.hk%2Fattachment%2Ftc%2Fedu-system%2Fprimary-secondary%2Fspa-systems%2Fprimary-1-admission%2Fschool-lists%2F2020dpnet-41.pdf&d=Fs4PzESj5DMZecC7Kr%2FqWP3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=7ee90770\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.edb.gov.hk/attachment/tc/edu-system/primary-secondary/spa-systems/primary-1-admission/school-lists/2020dpnet-41.pdf</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edf24e0e1377283c9959df5596d480cddca65fc3","tid":1703802,"uid":88284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T12:32:36.000Z","msg":"拉<br />\n支持驚察"},{"pid":"815958440cabfe2aac81f82c29c05b068375e5a5","tid":1703802,"uid":302878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T12:33:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1703677/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1703677/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n如果聽朝7點POLY集合,可以既報數<br />\n<br />\np牌推唔到"},{"pid":"92bde5729c9c7f17d310f20163b3b2a761f2fd4b","tid":1703802,"uid":88284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T12:34:10.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"b065d66f4146a8c5da8bba78d374ca4e1d